        <header data-points="4" data-reason="Interesting">
            <h3 class="comment-title" data-subject="Re:Basic summary:"><i class="com-toggle fa fa-caret-down"></i>Re:Basic summary:<span> (4, Interesting)</span></h3>
            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~TechyImmigrant" class="author" title="author name and user ID">TechyImmigrant (175943) </a> | about a year ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3598035&cid=43319069">(#43319069)</a></h4>
