            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~bcrowell" class="author" title="author name and user ID">bcrowell (177657) </a> | about a year ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3598035&cid=43321373">(#43321373)</a></h4>
